Subject: [PATCH 340/777] xprtrdma: Fix oops in Receive handler after device
 removal

commit 671c450b6fe0680ea1cb1cf1526d764fdd5a3d3f upstream.

Since v5.4, a device removal occasionally triggered this oops:

